<div class="container py-5"><div class="row justify-content-center"><div class="col-lg-8">
  <h1>About Craftify</h1>
  <p class="lead">Craftify is a marketplace connecting local artisans with customers who appreciate handmade, unique, and culturally rich products.</p>
  <hr>
  <h3>Our Mission</h3>
  <p>We empower local artisans in Bahrain and the Gulf region by providing them a platform to showcase and sell their handcrafted creations to a wider audience.</p>
  <h3>Why Choose Craftify?</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Authentic Craftsmanship</strong> - Every product is handmade by skilled local artisans</li>
    <li><strong>Supporting Local Communities</strong> - Your purchases directly support artisan livelihoods</li>
    <li><strong>Unique Products</strong> - Find one-of-a-kind items you won't find anywhere else</li>
    <li><strong>Live Auctions</strong> - Bid on exclusive handcrafted pieces in real-time</li>
  </ul>
  <h3>University Project</h3>
  <p>Craftify is developed as part of the ITCS489 Senior Project at the University of Bahrain, demonstrating a full-stack e-commerce solution with modern web technologies.</p>
</div></div></div>
